'''贝塔妮·休斯'''（Bettany Hughes，{{bd|1967年|5月||}}）<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Bettany Hughes|url=https://literature.britishcouncil.org/writer/bettany-hughes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709014427/https://literature.britishcouncil.org/writer/bettany-hughes|archive-date=2020-07-09|access-date=2020-07-18|website=British Council|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Bettany Mary Hugues|url=https://beta.companieshouse.gov.uk/officers/d-Sb1vYzvZbMf4Gr2TopyaJ-Qcc/appointments|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710183639/https://beta.companieshouse.gov.uk/officers/d-Sb1vYzvZbMf4Gr2TopyaJ-Qcc/appointments|archive-date=2020-07-10|access-date=2020-07-18|website=Companies House|dead-url=no}}</ref> 是一位英国历史学家、作家和广播员，专注于[[古典时代|古典时代]]历史。她出版的书籍大多是关于古典时代以及神话，但她也出版了伊斯坦布尔的历史。她积极鼓励在英国公立学校教授古典著作。

2019年，休斯获得[[大英帝国勋章|大英帝国勋章]]。

==早年生活和家庭==
贝塔妮生长于伦敦西区。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bettanyhughes.co.uk/about-bettany|title=About Bettany|work=bettanyhughes.co.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731040645/http://www.bettanyhughes.co.uk/about-bettany|archive-date=2013-07-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 她是演员彼得·休斯的女儿，也是板球运动员和记者西蒙·休斯的妹妹。她嫁给了阿德里安·埃文斯，生有两个孩子。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/my-perfect-weekend/8078810/My-perfect-weekend-Bettany-Hughes-historian.html|title=My perfect weekend: Bettany Hughes, historian|work=telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-date=2017-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215043536/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/my-perfect-weekend/8078810/My-perfect-weekend-Bettany-Hughes-historian.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她是一个素食者。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Silverman|first=Rosa|date=2017-10-20|title=Bettany Hughes on how the 'snowflake generation' may have cracked the work-life balance|language=en-GB|work=The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/women/life/bettany-hughes-generation-worked-every-hour-god-sent-todays/|access-date=2020-07-12|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712154656/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/women/life/bettany-hughes-generation-worked-every-hour-god-sent-todays/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

休斯于2019年被任命为大英帝国勋章。

==教育和职业==
休斯就读于[[伊灵|伊灵]]的诺丁山和伊灵中学，以及[[牛津大学圣希尔达学院|牛津大学圣希尔达学院]],获得古代和现代历史学位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.st-hildas.ox.ac.uk/bettany-hughes|title=Bettany Hughes|work=st-hildas.ox.ac.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818190740/http://www.st-hildas.ox.ac.uk/bettany-hughes|archivedate=2013-08-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

她是[[伦敦国王学院|伦敦国王学院]]客座研究员、[[加的夫大学|加的夫大学]]荣誉研究员、以及[[约克大学|约克大学]]荣誉博士<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.york.ac.uk/news-and-events/news/2013/events/honorary-degrees-january/|title=University awards five honorary degrees|work=york.ac.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723082642/https://www.york.ac.uk/news-and-events/news/2013/events/honorary-degrees-january/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
[[File:Ralph_Jackson_and_Bettany_Hughes.jpg|thumb]]

休斯编写并拍摄过许多关于古代和现代题材的纪录片和系列片。2009年，她被授予Naomi Sargant教育广播优秀特别奖，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vlv.org.uk/pages/VLVAwards2008.php|work=vlv.org.uk|title=VLV Awards 2009|accessdate=2013-10-14|url-status=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426042108/http://www.vlv.org.uk/pages/VLVAwards2008.php|archivedate=2012-04-26}}</ref> 2012年，她获得历史协会颁发的诺顿·姆德利科特奖，她是该协会的荣誉研究员<ref name="HA2012">{{cite web|title=The HA honours Bettany Hughes for services to History: Medlicott Medal 2012|url=http://www.history.org.uk/news/news_1433.html|work=HA News|publisher=The Historical Association|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220140424/http://history.org.uk/news/news_1433.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年，她参加[[倫敦大學皇家霍洛威學院|希腊学会]]的第十届年度讲座"Ta Erotika: The Things of Love",<ref name="Hell11">{{cite web|title=7 February 2011: Tenth Annual Hellenic Institute Lecture|url=http://www.rhul.ac.uk/hellenic-institute/news-and-events/|work=News and Events|publisher=Royal Holloway, University of London: The Hellenic Institute|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120422074600/http://www.rhul.ac.uk/Hellenic-Institute/News-and-Events/|archive-date=2012-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，2011年，她参加[[皇家电视学会|皇家电视学会]]的休·威尔顿纪念讲座，认为电视上的历史正处于繁荣的新的黄金时代<ref name="HWL11">{{cite web|title=Huw Wheldon Lecture 2011 with Bettany Hughes: TV – Modern Father of History|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0169lp5|work=Royal Television Society Lecture|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102105621/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0169lp5|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。2011年，她主持了[[百利女性小說獎|柑橘小说奖]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.orangeprize.co.uk/prize.html?v=180311#pj2011|title=ORANGE PRIZE FOR FICTION 2011 JUDGES ANNOUNCED|publisher=Orange Prize|accessdate=2011-07-03|archive-date=2013-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130222124022/http://www.orangeprize.co.uk/prize.html?v=180311#pj2011|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这是英国唯一一个女性小说年度图书奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.womensprizeforfiction.co.uk/about/history|title=History of the prize|work=womensprizeforfiction.co.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-date=2013-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622020430/http://www.womensprizeforfiction.co.uk/about/history|dead-url=no}}</ref>

休斯是艾里斯项目的赞助人，该项目在英国公立学校推广拉丁语和希腊语教学。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irismagazine.org/patrons.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-10-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004121210/http://www.irismagazine.org/patrons.html |archivedate=2011-10-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 她是Classics For All的名誉赞助人，这是一项全国性的运动，将古典语言和古代文明研究带回公立学校。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.classicsforall.org.uk/supporters/|title=Supporters|work=classicsforall.org.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|url-status=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105212706/http://www.classicsforall.org.uk/supporters/|archivedate=2013-11-05}}</ref> 她是科学、技术和文明基金会的顾问，该基金会旨在促进东西方之间的大型合作项目。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fstc.org.uk/aims-mission|title=Aims & Mission|work=fstc.org.uk|accessdate=2013-07-16|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225000712/http://www.fstc.org.uk/aims-mission|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2014年，她成为牛津大学的杰出校友<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sthildas.ox.ac.uk/dr-bettany-hughes-becomes-distinguished-friend-oxford|title=Dr Bettany Hughes becomes a Distinguished Friend of Oxford|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018081610/http://www.sthildas.ox.ac.uk/dr-bettany-hughes-becomes-distinguished-friend-oxford|archivedate=2014-10-18|url-status=yes|accessdate=2014-10-08}}</ref>。2016年，休斯发表了英国人文协会的年度伏尔泰演讲。<ref>{{Citation|last=British Humanist Association|title=The Voltaire Lecture 2016, with Bettany Hughes {{!}} Socrates, Confucius, and the Buddha|date=2016-05-25|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l3CBlLBLcUc|accessdate=2016-06-08|archive-date=2018-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528213655/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l3CBlLBLcUc|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，因对历史学的贡献而获得[[大英帝国勋章|大英帝国勋章]]<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=62666|supp=y|page=B12|date=8 June 2019}}</ref>。

==著作==
休斯写了四本书：
* 《特洛伊的海伦：女神、公主、妓女》（''Helen of Troy: Goddess, Princess, Whore''），2005年<ref name="BLcat">{{Cite web|title=British Library Item details|url=http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=013225329&con_lng=eng|access-date=2020-06-29|website=primocat.bl.uk|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701004621/http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=013225329&con_lng=eng|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 《[[毒堇之杯|毒堇之杯]]：苏格拉底，雅典和寻找美好的生活》（''The Hemlock Cup: Socrates, Athens and the Search for the Good Life''），2010年<ref name="BLcat2">{{Cite web|title=British Library Item details|url=http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=018515275&con_lng=eng|access-date=2020-06-29|website=primocat.bl.uk|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701171528/http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=018515275&con_lng=eng|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 《[[伊斯坦布尔三城记|伊斯坦布尔三城记]]》（''Istanbul : a tale of three cities''），2017年<ref name="BLcat3">{{Cite web|title=British Library Item details|url=http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=018913764&con_lng=eng|access-date=2020-06-29|website=primocat.bl.uk|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629225514/http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=018913764&con_lng=eng|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 《维纳斯和阿芙罗狄蒂》（''Venus and Aphrodite''），2019年<ref name="BLcat4">{{Cite web|title=British Library Item details|url=http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=019534281&con_lng=eng|access-date=2020-06-29|website=primocat.bl.uk|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629105101/http://primocat.bl.uk/F?func=direct&local_base=ITEMV&doc_number=019534281&con_lng=eng|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《毒堇之杯》一书被列入[[纽约时报畅销书榜|纽约时报畅销书榜]]，并被《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》选为年度图书<ref>{{cite news|date=2010-11-19|title=Books of the Year for Christmas: History|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/topics/christmas/8142784/Books-of-the-Year-for-Christmas-History.html|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724013134/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/topics/christmas/8142784/Books-of-the-Year-for-Christmas-History.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被[[BBC廣播四台|BBC廣播四台]]作为本周图书推荐<ref>{{cite web|title=Book of the Week: The Hemlock Cup: Socrates, Athens and the Search for the Good Life|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00wh306|accessdate=2012-04-11|work=Book of the Week|publisher=BBC Radio 4|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723093520/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00wh306|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并入围作家协会奖<ref>{{cite web|title=Writer's Guild Awards 2011|url=http://www.writersguild.org.uk/news-a-features/general/225-writers-guild-awards-2011-winners|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414233051/http://www.writersguild.org.uk/news-a-features/general/225-writers-guild-awards-2011-winners|archivedate=2012-04-14|accessdate=2013-10-14|work=writersguild.org.uk|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

《伊斯坦布尔三城记》获得[[纽约书评|纽约书评]]的关注<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Hansen|first=Suzy|date=2018-02-22|title=Istanbul Blues|url=https://www.nybooks.com/articles/2018/02/22/istanbul-blues/|journal=The New York Review of Books|volume=|pages=|via=|access-date=2020-07-23|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630225628/https://www.nybooks.com/articles/2018/02/22/istanbul-blues/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

